Usage: mark_physical_power_domains [-help] {-domains <string> | -reset | -checkOnly } [-domains <string> [-groupPhyLogicalDomains {{phyPd lpd1 lpd2 ...} ...}] ]

-help                              # Prints out the command usage
-checkOnly                         # do checking of fence sharing against P/G
                                   # nets (bool, required)
-domains <string>                  # name of domain with fence
                                   # (string, required)
-groupPhyLogicalDomains {{phyPd lpd1 lpd2 ...} ...}
                                   # list of domains (string, optional)
-reset                             # reset sharing setting (bool, required)